# Testing

- Swift Testing: @Test, @Suite, #expect, #require
- XCTest/XCUITest for UI tests
- Protocol-based fakes; no mocking frameworks
- Test naming: featureName_scenario_expectedResult
- @MainActor when testing @Observable ViewModels
